wingui NEWS
===========

Version 0.2
-----------
* Added opacity/transparency to WindowsGUI
* Added on.top to WindowsGUI
* Added read_lnk for reading windows shorcut files.
* Added win_processes for reading processes.
* Added win_users for listing logged on users
* Added win_load for listing the load on the CPU(s)
* Added win_kill for killing processes
* Added whos_the_hog for summarizing resource usage by users
* Added npptor, npp, and support functions find_npp, find_npptor
* Added is_r_startup

Version 0.1
-----------
* initial release
* allows changing the window title.
